{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775870355763,"sessionID":"ses_285e24e54ffeE9wMSq27VFW3fQ","part":{"id":"prt_d7a1f23e8001Wrycdc2QpPGWtf","messageID":"msg_d7a1f1457001aMUOMeSCXsSUu3","sessionID":"ses_285e24e54ffeE9wMSq27VFW3fQ","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_638df5848cb34b7eb3d055bc","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-029/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-029/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Delta Spec: AR-029 ŌĆö SDK HTTP Õ║ĢÕ▒éÕ«óµłĘń½»\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: *(Overview to be defined)*\n6: \n7: ## Base Specifications\n8: \n9: - **AR**: AR-029\n10: - **Module**: `sdk-python`\n11: - **Language**: Python\n12: - **Size**: M\n13: - **Base Specs**: `python-sdk/design.md`, `python-sdk/spec.md`\n14: \n15: ---\n16: \n17: ## Background\n18: \n19: *(Background to be defined)*\n20: \n21: ---\n22: \n23: ## Requirements\n24: \n25: *(Requirements to be defined)*\n26: \n27: ---\n28: \n29: ## Non-Requirements\n30: \n31: *(Explicitly out of scope items to be defined)*\n32: \n33: ---\n34: \n35: ## Dependencies\n36: \n37: | Dependency | Description |\n38: |------------|-------------|\n39: | AR-028 | AgentRuntimeClient implementation |\n40: | python-sdk/design.md | Base SDK design document |\n41: | python-sdk/spec.md | Base specification |\n42: \n43: ---\n44: \n45: ## Acceptance Criteria\n46: \n47: | ID | Criterion | Verification Method |\n48: |----|-----------|---------------------|\n49: | *(AC to be defined) | | |\n50: \n51: ---\n52: \n53: ## Test Strategy\n54: \n55: *(Test strategy to be defined)*\n56: \n57: ---\n58: \n59: ## Implementation Notes\n60: \n61: *(Implementation notes to be defined)*\n\n(End of file - total 61 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Delta Spec: AR-029 ŌĆö SDK HTTP Õ║ĢÕ▒éÕ«óµłĘń½»\n\n## Overview\n\n*(Overview to be defined)*\n\n## Base Specifications\n\n- **AR**: AR-029\n- **Module**: `sdk-python`\n- **Language**: Python\n- **Size**: M\n- **Base Specs**: `python-sdk/design.md`, `python-sdk/spec.md`\n\n---\n\n## Background\n\n*(Background to be defined)*\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-029/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775870355753,"end":1775870355761}}}}
